ched website!</li></ul></div></div></div></div><div id="container-footer"><div id="page-footer"><div id="footer-nav"><nav class="left"><ul><li class="active"><a href="//dotabuff.com/pages/changelog">English</a></li><li class=""><a href="//ru.dotabuff.com/pages/changelog">Русский</a></li><li class=""><a href="//zh.dotabuff.com/pages/changelog">中文</a></li><li class=""><a href="//pt.dotabuff.com/pages/changelog">Português</a></li></ul></nav><nav class="right"><ul><li><a href="/pages/about">About</a></li><li><a href="/pages/changelog">Changelog</a></li><li><a href="/pages/privacy">Privacy</a></li><li><a href="/pages/about#support">Support</a></li><li><a href="https://twitter.com/dotabuff" data-track-outgoing="true" target="_blank">Twitter</a></li></ul></nav><div>Copyright 2012 Elo Entertainment LLC. Dota 2 is a registered trademark of Valve Corporation.</div></div></div></div><div class="modal" id="plus-feature" style="display: none"><section><header class="premium">Dotabuff Plus</header><footer style="max-width: 600px"><p><em>This feature is only available to Dotabuff Plus members.</em></p><p style="padding: 8px 0 0 0">Support from Plus members keep Dotabuff running and help enable us to deliver new features for everyone. As a reward, some features that are difficult or expensive to operate are available only to Plus members.</p><p style="padding: 12px 0 0 0"><a href="/plus" class="button premium">Tell me more...</a> <a href="/plus" class="button cancel simplemodal-close">Nevermind</a></p></footer></section></div><script type="text/javascript">
